title: Bikerumor Pic Of The Day: Elizabeth River – Norfolk, Virginia
content:
Photo submitted by Michael Willits, “My friend and I snapped this twilight photo on an abandoned quay along the Elizabeth River in Norfolk, VA. We’d been racing the waning sunlight back home and were rewarded with getting to watch a beautiful sunset across the water.” We always love seeing photos from where you are riding […]
